In bullish trend, we will look to buy in discount zone and sell in premium zone in bullish trending market.
Similarly, we will sell in discount zone and buy in premium zone for bearish trend.
Remember, any trading setup designed in discounted zone will be high probability setup and similarly,
any setup in premium zone will be low probability.
Next, we can use these PD zones to formulate a setup in trend continuation markets.
We can use these zones on retracement, or you can say that on pullback phase significantly in trending market.
